<http://www.spektrix.com/capilanouniversity/event/12601ADHGSMRHJGRGJSDPTNTCRCGQHPQN>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "CapU Choirs: In the Same Room";
  schema:description """
	CapU Choirs’ In the Same Room concert brings voices into conversation across cultures, traditions, and time. Baroque excerpts by Vivaldi meet musical worlds of the East and works by Indigenous composers resonate through the choral voice. Wonderful popular favourites enter the dialogue, asking timeless questions of purpose and becoming. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Inspired by the late Stó:lō First Nations  Elder Lee Maracle’s reminder that we must be in the same room to create a shared future, this evening asks: now that we’re here, what do we make together?<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://capilanoumusic.ca/events\">CapU Music Website</a><span><br/></span>
""";
