<http://www.spektrix.com/capilanouniversity/event/4401APLLPBSHLDJVTLGBDQTQBHJDJSHCM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Tord Gustavsen Trio";
  schema:description """
	<h2>Tord Gustavsen Trio takes place at Christ Church Cathedral</h2><span><br/></span>The Norwegian pianist and composer Tord Gustavsen is on a constant search for honest beauty in music. He strives to deliver a holy trinity of emotional intensity, elegance, and mediative musical experience.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For Gustavsen’s concert in the magnificent Christ Church Cathedral, his trio, including Jarle Vespestad and bassist/electronics manipulator Steiner Raknes. will perform music from their latest record <span class=\"ItalicText\">Seeing</span>. The album brims with innovative approaches to sound and technique while creating intricately textured improvisations and understated melodic hooks.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Audience members can expect Gustavsen, who has released ten albums, to create an experience of spiritual depth and intimacy in an immaculate performance full of beauty. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-jhOaf_refA\">Watch Tord Gustavsen Trio - The Other Side</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>“Spiritual depth and intimacy ... also moments when the music felt more rock-centered, exhibiting great grooves. It was a flawless concert, full of beautiful experiences.” <span class=\"ItalicText\">JazzTrail</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.capilanou.ca/student-services/community/blueshore-financial-centre-for-the-performing-arts/our-events/all-events/events/tord-gustavsen-trio.php\">Show Info</a></h2><span><br/></span><h2><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.thecathedral.ca/programs/plan-your-visit\">Christ Church Cathedral Parking Info</a></h2>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-03-17T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/capilanouniversity/files/65202db9-5e4e-4516-a335-2b2b92d13cda.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/capilanouniversity/location/801ARDQDDMGGJKKRTNTJBMCCMMBCPQKCR>;
  schema:organizer <https://spektrix.com/capilanouniversity/organization/blueshore-financial-centre-for-the-performing-arts>;
